525
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:17,000
We from the Beggar's Sect never judge one's appearance and origin.

526
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:21,000
We will only respect those who are good at martial arts and responsible.

527
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:23,600
I think you have excellent martial arts.

528
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:25,100
Why don't you join the Beggar's Sect?

529
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:27,700
We can travel together. That way, we can watch each other's back.

530
00:37:27,700 --> 00:37:29,400
Won't that be better?

531
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:32,800
Brother, are you serious?

532
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:35,100
Of course.

533
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:38,800
