535
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:45,200
But I promised Miss A'Zi to send her back to Liao.

536
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:48,200
Just now, I wanted to ask if you could lend us a carriage

537
00:37:48,200 --> 00:37:50,400
to be on our way.

538
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:52,700
Are you sending for a famous physician

539
00:37:52,700 --> 00:37:54,800
to help Miss A'Zi to cure her eyes?

540
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:57,400
You can really tell.

541
