Miss A'Zi has family in the Liao Kingdom who has great influence

542
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:02,400
unlike me who has nothing.

543
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,200
If I send Miss A'Zi back,

544
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:07,600
the chances will be higher to treat her eyes.

545
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:11,400
